fields.title: HackathonAfrica 3.0 Web Foundations Assessment
fields.description: This assessment is designed to evaluate fundamental web development skills in HTML, CSS, and basic JavaScript. The test covers essential concepts such as structuring web pages with HTML, styling with CSS, and adding interactivity with JavaScript. It aims to gauge the readiness of applicants for the HackathonAfrica 3.0 program, ensuring they have the foundational knowledge necessary to excel in the bootcamp.
